body_html: This was a terrible way to post what I thought was a bug. I think I just lacked data, and the model when run on my Windows PC proved useless anyways. I'd just advise whoever runs into a bus error running nasnet_mobile to try some other better suited model like mobilenet in tfhub. Keep plugging more data and toy with the hyperparams.
